Sap - blade utilty skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Sap allows you to tap into the spirits of fallen
Swashbucklers. Performing this action will bind a part of
that otherworldy energy onto a blade, allowing for a quick
slash against an opponent. When the blade makes contact,
the attacker will drain some of the target's dexterity.
More experienced Swashbucklers will gain more from the
maneuver.

GL:  14
SP:  25
command:  ssap <target>
duration: 30+ seconds

